quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  14,43,"Tuma nde yim…ďe …ďen immintinaa e genaale ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe yaccora ka noddu…óo On, hara hi…ďe Ňčalliniri ko'e ma…ď…ďe …óen ka weeyo, ndaar…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ruttotaako e ma…ď…ďe, ko non …óe heddorta e kulol ko …óe yi'ata. Hara …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen yeewu…óe, …óe haqqiltaa …óe faamataa, hakkee …óen∆īere."
  14,44,"An Nulaa…óo, jertiniri mofte maa …óen lepte Alla …óen √Ďalnde Darngal, too√Īirnoo…ďe ko'e-mun …ďen yeddu- gol Alla sirkana Mo wi'oya ontuma: Joomi amen, nennan men, nennitanaa men lepte …óen, ruttitaa men aduna yeru dumunna hawru…óo, men gom…óine, men jokka Nulaa…ďe …ďe immin-…óaa …ďen e amen. ∆Āe jaaboree feloore: E on laatanooki on woondiino ka aduna, wonnde onon on iwataa e …óam nguurndam aduna yahon laakara, yeddu…óon immital …ďaawo maayde?"
  14,45,"Ho…óu…óon e ko…óooli mofte adinoo…ďe …ďen too√Īir…ďe ko'e mun yeddugol Alla, wano yim…ďe Huudi e yim…ďe Saalih. ∆Āanngani on kadi ko Men huuwi …ďe kon e halakuyee, Men piyirani on mise ka Deftere Alla no waajitoron, kono on waajitoraaki."
  14,46,"Gom…óii …ďee ho…óu…ďe e ko…óooli mofte adinoo…ďe …ďen too√Īu…ďe fewjii fii warugol Annabiijo Muhammadu (yo o his), …ďe bonna fii noddaandu makko ndun. Alla non no anndi fii fewjoore ma…ď…ďe nden, huunde suu…óaaki Mo e mayre, fewjoore ma…ď…ďe ko lo'unde; nde irtirtaa lo'ere mayre pelle maa go…ó…óum goo, yeeso fewjoore Alla nden e ma…ď…ďe."
  14,47,"Wata a sikku an Nulaa…óo, wonnde Alla lunndoto fodoore nde O fodiri Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen poolal e …ďannginnde diina kan. Pellet, Alla ko Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake, ma O semmbin yi…ó…ďe Makko …ďen, ko O Jom yottorgol no sattiri e a√Īu…ďe Mo …ďen e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen."
  14,48,"Ngol yoftagol e heefer…ďe …ďen, ko √Ďalnde Darngal wa…óata, √Īalnde ndii leydi wa…ótitirtee leydi goo raneeri laa…ďundi, kammuuli …óin kadi wa…ótitiree go…ó…ói goo. Yim…ďe …ďen fee√Īira e genaale ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďalli ma…ď…ďe e golle ma…ď…ďe, fii no darora yeeso Heeror…óo laamu e mawngu Mun, Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake."
  14,49,"An Nulaa…óo, a yi'oyay √Īalnde leydi ndin wa…ótitiroya leydi goo, kammuli …óin wa…ótitee, yi'aa heefer…ďe …ďen e sirkoo…ďe …ďen hino ha…ď…ďindiraa e kolombooje, …ďe humindiree juu…óe e koy…óe ma…ď…ďe haa ka daa…óe callale. Conci ma…ď…ďe …ói …ďe …ďoornotoo …óin ko e mbollam (…óum ko ko hu…ď…ďata ooya) geece ma…ď…ďe …ďaleeji …óen suddiree yiite."
  14,50,"An Nulaa…óo, a yi'oyay √Īalnde leydi ndin wostora leydi goo, kammuli …óin wa…ótitee, yi'aa heefer…ďe …ďen e sirkoo…ďe …ďen hino ha…ď…ďindiraa e kolombooje, …ďe humindiree juu…óe e koy…óe ma…ď…ďe haa ka daa…óe callale. Conci ma…ď…ďe …ói …ďe …ďoornotoo …óin ko e mbollam (…óum ko ko hu…ď…ďata ooya) geece ma…ď…ďe …ďaleeje …óen suddiree yiite."
  14,51,"∆äum fow ko fii no Alla yo…ďira kala wonkii ko ki golli e mo∆ī∆īere maa bone. Pellet, Alla ko yaawu…óo hasbugol golle."
  14,52,"Ndee Alqur'aaaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo o his) ko nulal Alla e yim…ďe …ďen, e fii yo …ďe hulu kammbaaji mayre tii…óu…óe, e no …ďe anndirar ewetee- …óo e goonga alaa si wanaa Alla Gooto On, …ďe rewa Mo hara …ďe kafidaali Mo e go…ó…óo goo, e no joomi- raa…ďe haqqille hisu…óe …ďen waajitora nde …ďe taskoo, tawde ko kam…ďe nafitorta waaju mayre."